{"tid":2377002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始姑娘入限制區被警喝停 徐英偉解圍「職員嚟」","createTime":"2021-01-23T08:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T03:03:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":221,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"5b16d92ed2b0ec64455f4755a555a23d27923b41","tid":2377002,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"政府今日（23日）凌晨宣布喺佐敦劃「受限區域」，要求區內居民做新型冠狀病毒檢測，並且要全區完成晒先可以離開。環境局長黃錦星、食物及衛生局長陳肇始同埋民政事務局長徐英偉今朝到場視察，不過陳肇始入區時無掛證件，一度被駐守嘅警員截停，要其他官員幫忙先入到<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始今朝同徐英偉，以及衛生署長陳漢儀行入受限區嗰陣，帶頭嘅徐英偉同殿後嘅陳漢儀都有掛上證件，陳肇始就冇。把守住受限區鐵馬嘅「士沙」（警署警長）隨即就截停咗佢，當陳肇始想攞翻張證出嚟畀「士沙」睇之際，徐英偉同陳漢儀好快就幫口話「職員嚟」，然後陳肇始先獲放行。"},{"pid":"651b5f6809ee8bfdc3c03e631f83eab19269d412","tid":2377002,"uid":14965,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今朝新聞來"},{"pid":"52efb0f044eb1d5006c3e4280c744770672d0046","tid":2377002,"uid":28237,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"連個士沙都唔俾面你呀"},{"pid":"8476d3d07abb30ef3097c5cb7fa7b5843a305a93","tid":2377002,"uid":79993,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"最好之後見佢又無帶證件唔俾佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fa9ca13ad19a2db7194e463cfaaa1088296a59","tid":2377002,"uid":135390,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"想睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇link"},{"pid":"cb5bb698c5d305b4c58a7ad8d21e18049e21193e","tid":2377002,"uid":381575,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"你邊撚度㗎"},{"pid":"facee8f9ea2b9dea227cb4a72da0cc51aec5bc47","tid":2377002,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96edaadd08b4dd75